<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>نَسَبهُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> محمدُ بنُ عُقْبةَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُنكَرُ الحديثِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَن <span class="c2">(٣)</span> أبي التّيَّاحِ، وإسْرائيلَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>هو البَصْريُّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢٩٩٦]</span> حمَّادُ بنُ الجَعْدِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> <span class="c2">(٦)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>سمعَ قَتادةَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>سمعَ مِنه هُدْبةُ البَصريُّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
